    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't know about \"growth\" though. it doesn't feel like a gap or a transition. it just feels like the lights went out a long time ago. it's like i'm just occupying space that doesn't belong to me anymore. there's nothing left inside to actually grow. it's just hollow.",
